Seoul this year.
</P>
<P>
Putin has decided to pay an official visit to the Republic of
Korea"some time in 2000," and the specific date will be agreed
upon through diplomatic channels, Russian Foreign Minister Igor
Ivanov told a news conference, after his meeting with South Korean
