dialogue and cooperation" and "will contribute to creating trust
on the peninsula," he said.
</P>
<P>
The summit "has further weakened the arguments of those who
advocate the creation of a national anti-missile defense system,"
he noted, urging that "the Korean Peninsula should be turned into
a nuclear-free zone."
</P>
<P>
The agenda of Putin's visit to DPRK slated for July will
include bilateral relations, security and stability in the Korean
Peninsula and in the whole Asian-Pacific region, Ivanov said.
</P>
