<HEADLINE> 1st Five-Star Hotel to Open in Bangladesh by 2002 </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
DHAKA, June 29 (Xinhua) -- The first five-star hotel in the
private sector is expected to begin operation in the first half of
2002 in Bangladesh, The Financial Express reported here Thursday.
</P>
