Certificate on quality and is applying for the ISO14001
Certificate, which is concerned with the impact on the environment.
</P>
<P>
In line with the central government's call to develop western
regions, ABB Group invested 73 million U.S. dollars in Chongqing
in 1998, which is the only provincial-level municipality in
western China, to manufacture energy converting equipment.
